article_title: New Pharmacies And PBM Growth Boost CVS Health Profits

article_metadata.description: Buoyed by the addition of new employer clients for its pharmacy benefit management business, Target pharmacies and the Omnicare specialty pharmacy business, CVS Health said profits jumped 13% in last year's fourth quarter. The giant drugstore chain, which added 1,600 Target pharmacies last year, reported net income of nearly $1.5 billion [...]
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
